## Don't Do

- ❌ Create interfaces for single implementations
- ❌ Add null checks everywhere
- ❌ Wrap everything in try-catch
- ❌ Add logging to every function
- ❌ Create DTOs for simple data
- ❌ Make everything configurable
- ❌ Use async when not needed
- ❌ Invent new patterns

## Do

- ✅ Grep for existing patterns first
